memory_warning_modal.old_browser_out_of_.string: Try updating your browser to the latest version or open the file in the Figma desktop app to recover content in this file.

rcs.pro_trials_onboarding.unlimited_page.string: You can add more than {maxFreePages} pages to this file. Just click into the Pages menu and select the +.

rcs.pro_trials_onboarding.component_publ.string: Select the {teamLibraryIcon} icon to open the library panel.
Select {createComponentIcon} in the tool bar (or {createComponentShortcut}) to turn it into a component.

rcs.pro_trials_onboarding.video_subtitle.string: Select {imageOrVideoIcon} to bulk-add videos. (You can also drag videos from your computer onto the canvas.)

pro_onboarding.use_variables_in_componen.string: Use variables in components and prototypes to toggle light/dark mode, localize language, and more.

pro_onboarding.change_who_can_edit_and_v.string: Change who can edit and view your files on your Professional plan.

pro_onboarding.now_that_you_re_on_a_prof.string: Now that you’re on a Professional team, move your files into project folders to keep things tidy.

pro_onboaridng.you_now_get_unlimited_des.string: Hooray! You now get unlimited design files, pages, and FigJam boards.
Hooray! You now get unlimited design files and unlimited pages inside them.

pro_onboarding.on_your_professional_plan.string: On your Professional plan, you can share prototypes without sharing the rest of your design file.

pro_onboarding.if_you_want_to_reach_a_de.string: If you want to reach a decision, keep things simple with a FigJam vote.

pro_onboarding.if_other_people_are_in_yo.string: If other people are in your file, select the headphones to start an audio chat.

rcs.pro_trials_onboarding.audio_subtitle.string: Invite your teammates to this file.

rcs.pro_trials_onboarding.open_sessions_.string: Try an open session with logged-out users.

rcs.pro_trials_onboarding.component_publ.string: In the current file section, select the “{publishButtonText}” button.
Select UI that you want to reuse, like buttons and icons.
Components help you design more quickly and create consistency across files.

multiplayer_upgrade_modal.title.string: A new version of Figma is available!

multiplayer_upgrade_modal.content.string: We’ll save all your work, but you need to reload to see edits from other users.

multiplayer_upgrade_modal.content_offlin.string: We can't reach our servers right now. Please make sure you are connected to the internet to reload.
